{"tid":609711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[No IT] IT男開發麻將賭博手機App被捕","createTime":"2018-03-29T09:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T12:19:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bed99a222aa772fb445ac133e855658d8adee7e3","tid":609711,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T09:11:11.000Z","msg":"在上海一間公司擔任IT技術員的萬某某辭職後創業，開發出一款名為「鎮江全民麻將」的App。他透過出售代幣「鑽石」，半年多時間，竟然獲利高達550多萬元（人民幣，下同）。<br />\n<br />\n不過，由於該手機App具有賭博性質，引起江蘇鎮江警方展開行動，拘捕萬某某等二十多名相關者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1315903/org/c4712cd85050d72979433aaa4a3d2a67.jpg/onyzlmE0e8G-_Js4SDU3sIQx3EiKrCbMkOtwZ5DrcGc?v=w1440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1315903%2Forg%2Fc4712cd85050d72979433aaa4a3d2a67.jpg%2FonyzlmE0e8G-_Js4SDU3sIQx3EiKrCbMkOtwZ5DrcGc%3Fv%3Dw1440&h=e3880c74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/173092/it%E7%94%B7%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC%E9%BA%BB%E5%B0%87%E8%B3%AD%E5%8D%9A%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9Fapp%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%A9%E9%80%BE550%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%B9%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F173092%2Fit%25E7%2594%25B7%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%25B3%25AD%25E5%258D%259A%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259Fapp%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%2588%25A9%25E9%2580%25BE550%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B9%25A3&d=oizoEBJqYhngY9Rq5Z2et8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=77b27ba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/173092/it%E7%94%B7%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC%E9%BA%BB%E5%B0%87%E8%B3%AD%E5%8D%9A%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9Fapp%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E7%8D%B2%E5%88%A9%E9%80%BE550%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91